task.summary:
Fixed HashMap<Point, Cell> bug.
Used java built in point instead of Point class.

Ultimate Design - PhysicalEntity added
Design based on mhaghighat20 design

Changed scheduling order.
After adding physical entity it was necessary to integrate timer in the physical entity.

Added point lookup to physical entity.
Now can get cells hashmap by PhysicalEntity.getArea()

Adopted the implementation partially with the ultimate design
Integrated paths to map.

Added configuration and map simple files.
The map template is designed.

Added simple map.
Now maps can be created from xml files. A simple xml map is in data directory.

Implemented command processor.
Added command actions and related world functions.
Added start functionality to command processor.
Added timer tick and timer task to physical entity
Added timer itself and timer facility.
Refactored some codes and added world.start

First scheduled output.
The Gate.timerTick() is working and printing the gate is beating. Now we have to refactor this code and make it a good structure for future use.
Edited gitignore from an online version.
